{"tid":2285574,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃圈流通代幣提議 - USDT","createTime":"2020-11-14T08:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T10:25:55.000Z","uid":174301,"like":4,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8a214b4ce36c61f134ff9eeeafb5cc63bc7e7b17","tid":2285574,"uid":174301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:19:14.000Z","msg":"主要會用兩種: 交易用的USDT 同 加密通訊用ZCASH<br />\nUSDT是能夠做 1USDT : 1USDT ， 當中「零式」是能夠為各位會員提供一兌一服務。<br />\n<br />\n為了確保該條款可以被執行，每輸入100USD到「零式」， 「零式」便會支付101 USDT 到入款者手上。反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n 例: 小明人金100 USD ， 手上銀包會顯示101 USDT。<br />\n<br />\n       若小明入金101USDT ，「零式」亦會轉移100USD到他戶口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/16boREAohCBVtUM8KohMHdtLoF8mU_BNPmrzhp29uQ7Q/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F16boREAohCBVtUM8KohMHdtLoF8mU_BNPmrzhp29uQ7Q%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=5a2ac61b\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/16boREAohCBVtUM8KohMHdtLoF8mU_BNPmrzhp29uQ7Q/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"6710bc3938b65ebb92936b70910c2e8f0afb4685","tid":2285574,"uid":60977,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"行撚開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9367ba47a25d11e95c2bd2913460ae40338325","tid":2285574,"uid":47142,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:23:42.000Z","msg":"G持用stablecoin  一齊拋港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42f48ccee194825b8d638ec009e8e1888951c71","tid":2285574,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"入去傾<br />\nBitcoin / Ethereum / Crypto 集中討論區 (5)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2270166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2270166</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"17753382865ac567003403c4f6bd819f8b5eaeb8","tid":2285574,"uid":17430